{"type": "article", "id": 47382, "title": "1930 年代电台用的台灯重新推出，样子依然时髦｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-11-19T23:16:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 2263, "name": "台灯"}, {"id": 922, "name": "电动车"}, {"id": 3257, "name": "瓷砖"}, {"id": 40208, "name": "休闲椅"}, {"id": 3563, "name": "办公家具"}, {"id": 45618, "name": "Bisazza"}, {"id": 45619, "name": "Torrot"}, {"id": 41133, "name": "Louis Poulsen"}, {"id": 45620, "name": "True Design"}, {"id": 45621, "name": "Utopia Arkitekter"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 112, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171119152020rjeRGXLY4b0BMFKH.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; background-color: #ffffff} span.s4 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; background-color: #ffffff} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s7 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s8 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Skýli Mountain Shelter by Utopia Arkitekter</h3><p>斯德哥尔摩工作室 Utopia Arkitekter 最近设计了一款帐篷状的临时住房，名为 Skýli，位于冰岛，可以承受当地的极端天气条件。它由钢材和交叉层压木板制成，最多可容纳 15 名登山者，并有额外的空间用于烹饪、晾晒衣物和储存物品。</p><p>整个小屋是由四个尖角金字塔形成，旨在提供结构的稳定性，形状也类似于传统的冰岛小屋，而明亮的蓝色是对冰岛首都雷克雅未克（Reykjavík）丰富多彩建筑的回应。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152050FNVJaKR58h7j2wSq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152052O7MFPSs1tixEwdca.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706853\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152052ITqefvcp6OtmJSs4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.442893\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711191520522NqgUtEnYTsWeP3j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.895516\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152053HqT534kX2isyG1BY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.442893\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152056PdXuE9jVos7qz5lp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.892132\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.utopia.se/se/projekt/skyli\" rel=\"nofollow\">Utopia Arkitekter</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>“True Goes Through” collection by True Design</h3><p>True Design 是意大利一个新兴的家具品牌，专门为家庭、办公室和酒店环境提供办公家具。在今年的伦敦 100% 设计展上，他们推出了新系列 True Goes Through，配色灵感来自 Paul Klee 的绘画作品。</p><p>Orlandini Design 设计的 ARCA 椅适用于休息室和等候区域；DNA 长凳是特别的螺旋样式，每一个螺旋形成一个独立的座位，由 Leonardo Rossano 和 Debora Mansur 设计；由 Parisotto + Formenton 设计的 MILLEPIEDI 是一种模块化的座椅系统；Luciano Dell’Orefice 设计的 PINCETTES 是一个声音分隔器，提供隐私的同时，不隔离用户。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152205mIGQDBR70jhb6L8U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.643750\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152205qQrt3b60AJgYPsC7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.644531\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152206o29rBmuDHT1S0h3t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414365\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152206gC2fKbBvxD7MP6AE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.417497\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152206yvFwVeadPGfl9B7z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.643750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711191522075qjFuT8bSoe9kdc7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.truedesign.it/products.php\" rel=\"nofollow\">True Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>VL38 Table Lamp by Vilhelm Lauritzen for Louis Poulsen</h3><p>1930 年代，丹麦建筑师 Vilhelm Lauritzen 为哥本哈根广播电台创造了一盏工作用的台灯 VL38，它的样式简洁经典，如今看来仍不过时，且充满复古感。最近，丹麦灯具品牌 Louis Poulsen 重新推出了 VL38 的最新版本，黑色和铬的组合看着很高级。售价 370 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152508Cel8GQRZM0z41iHn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152508ZkgmxSbKdANqVMvy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152508Vlh6uBiYTmc4tz5E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152508a4AeNpvm2FlWf3tJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.595725\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.louispoulsen.com/asia/products/indoor/table/vl38-table/c-24/c-1423/p-66233\" rel=\"nofollow\">Louis Poulsen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Eddy Lounge Chair by Alain Gilles</h3><p>这把名为 Eddy 的休闲椅，名字源自比利时著名自行车手 Eddy Merckx，是比利时设计师 Alain Gilles 为意大利品牌 Bonaldo 而设计。它的管状金属结构让人想起优雅的老式竞赛自行车。Eddy 的各部件通过使用快速释放锁来连接，这种锁通畅用于将车轮固定在自行车车架上。Eddy 的可定制元素包括头枕，挂在扶手上的皮革侧袋等等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152737DW0nolO8b52YIzPJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152738aQJV1ZFHPUriWye5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.599831\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152739OF1qabsr2gl4jSkU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.475042\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711191527405FCVtib9ejlPEpDH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152740r8o5czTDqYlJt9Up.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.176819\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152742bfUo7lKPt95Vrg8F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2017/11/18/alain-gilles-eddy-lounge-chair-bonaldo-references-vintage-bicycles/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Torrot Velocipedo by Torrot</h3><p>西班牙电动摩托车制造商 Torrot 最近推出了新品 Torrot Velocipedo，是一款介于轻便摩托车和汽车之间的三轮混合型机车，被描述为“下一代电动互联化交通工具，希望改变城市之间的机动性”。Torrot Velocipedo 配备功率 13.5 马力的电动机，保证舒适与安全。Torrot 品牌为这款机车设计的广告词为“像摩托车一样敏捷，和汽车一样安全”。机车配备 8 千瓦时的电池组，充电时间仅需 4.3 小时，单次充电可行驶 150 公里，最高时速 55公里。</p><p>它不仅排放量为 0，车身配备的彩色显示屏，可显示包括车速、温度等信息，还可通过无线或 USB 接口与 iOS 系统及 Android 系统移动设备进行同步。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152852IXoaKN9T4d5ABbuG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711191528524JESi61nCAuyYfrb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.508557\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152853ViOeA0NfmwEB2URh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.645477\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Tonal collection by David Rockwell </h3><p>意大利设计品牌 Bisazza 擅长制造那些样式复杂的瓷砖。最近，他们与美国设计师 David Rockwell 合作，推出了 Tonal 系列瓷砖，由四种不同色系的图案组合而成，为 Bisazza 的艺术系列 Cementiles 添入了现代主义美学的元素。大胆的色彩纹理和生动的线条，可以通过多种方式进行组合，从一种颜色跳跃到另一种颜色，像是在制造一场幻觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711191529232DXkrFvWY9uKBgl0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612987\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152923Ve80qaEM1iKRrIy6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612987\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152924KpfJencMIXma2yVj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.737500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152925zaSsYduBlp018nKh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.737500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152925mI8ixbSPUE4rRqA1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.737500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171119152925OUe2ft3w4gshEbI8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.737500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.wallpaper.com/design/david-rockwell-x-bisazza-tile-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Wallpaper*</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}